        "min": 1,
        "max": 10,
        "value": 2,
        "unit": "passes",
        "description": "Single pass for light contamination, multi-pass for heavy; 2 passes recommended for complete removal on Lanthanum while minimizing risk to soft substrate. Source: Industry case studies in laser cleaning of metals (e.g., Proc. SPIE 2019) and practical guidelines from Adapt Laser Systems."
      },
